Package de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.core

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Definition
    Definition is a class representing a narrative description of a Sense.
    GlobalInformation
    GlobalInformation is a class representing administrative information and other general attributes of a LexicalResource.
    LexicalEntry
    LexicalEntry is a class representing a lexeme in a given language.
    LexicalResource
    LexicalResource is a class representing the entire resource.
    Lexicon
    Lexicon is a class containing all the lexical entries of a given language within the entire resource.
    Sense
    Sense is a class representing one meaning of a lexical entry.
    The Sense class allows for hierarchical senses in that a sense may be more specific than another sense of the same lexical entry.
    Statement
    Statement is a class representing a narrative description and refines or complements Definition.
    TextRepresentation
    TextRepresentation is a class representing one textual content of Definition or Statement.
